name pgfopts
category Package
revision 77682
shortdesc LaTeX package options with pgfkeys
longdesc The pgfkeys package (part of the pgf distribution) is a
longdesc well-designed way of defining and using large numbers of keys
longdesc for key-value syntaxes. However, pgfkeys itself does not offer
longdesc means of handling LaTeX class and package options. This package
longdesc adds such option handling to pgfkeys, in the same way that
longdesc kvoptions adds the same facility to the LaTeX standard keyval
longdesc package.
